1. *Budala* je uvijek u potrazi za novim zabavama. (The fool is always looking for new amusements.)
2. On se ponaša kao *budala*. (He is behaving like a fool.)
3. *Budalom* naziva sve one koji mu se ne sviđaju. (He calls everyone he doesn't like a fool.)
4. *Budalo* je pustio da ga prevare. (The fool let himself be deceived.)
5. Ona je *budala* što je to uradila. (She is a fool for having done that.)